          Suspendisse dictum feugiat nisl ut dapibus. Mauris iaculis porttitor
          posuere. Praesent id metus massa, ut blandit odio.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="clear-both mb-8">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">
          Floating Style + Square Aspect Ratio + Right Position
        </h3>
        <Image
          src={sampleImage}
          alt="Floating style with square aspect ratio and right position"
          title=">Floating style with square aspect ratio"
          style="floating"
          aspectRatio="square"
          position="right"
        />
        <p class="mb-4">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam in dui
          mauris. Vivamus hendrerit arcu sed erat molestie vehicula. Sed auctor
          neque eu tellus rhoncus ut eleifend nibh porttitor. Ut in nulla enim.
          Phasellus molestie magna non est bibendum non venenatis nisl tempor.
          Suspendisse dictum feugiat nisl ut dapibus. Mauris iaculis porttitor
          posuere. Praesent id metus massa, ut blandit odio.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="clear-both mb-8">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">
          Bordered Style + Video Aspect Ratio + Full Position
        </h3>
        <Image
          src={sampleImage}
          alt="Bordered style with video aspect ratio and full position"
          title="_Bordered style with video aspect ratio and full position"
          style="bordered"
          aspectRatio="video"
          position="full"
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">
        Invert Options (Dark Mode Only)
      </h2>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">
          Inverted Image (Using invert prop)
        </h3>
        <p class="mb-2 text-sm text-muted">
          Note: Inversion only applies in dark mode. Switch to dark mode to see
          the effect.
        </p>
        <Image
          src={sampleImage}
          alt="Inverted image using prop"
          title="Inverted image using invert prop"
          invert={true}
        />
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">
          Inverted Image (Using ! control character)
        </h3>
        <p class="mb-2 text-sm text-muted">
          Note: Inversion only applies in dark mode. Switch to dark mode to see
          the effect.
        </p>
        <Image
          src={sampleImage}
          alt="Inverted image using control character"
          title="!This image is inverted using the ! control character"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">
          Combined: Invert + Style + Effect
        </h3>
        <Image
          src={sampleImage}
          alt="Inverted image with glass style and zoom effect"
          title="!Inverted image with glass style and zoom effect"
          style="glass"
          effect="zoom"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">
          Combined: Invert + Left Position
        </h3>
        <Image
          src={sampleImage}
          alt="Inverted image with left position"
          title="!<Inverted image with left position"
        />
        <p class="mb-4">
          This example demonstrates combining the invert prefix (!) with a
          position control character (&lt;). The image is both inverted and
          positioned to the left. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur
          adipiscing elit. Nullam in dui mauris. Vivamus hendrerit arcu sed erat
          molestie vehicula.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="clear-both mb-8">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">
          Combined: Invert + Right Position
        </h3>
        <Image
          src={sampleImage}
          alt="Inverted image with right position"
          title="!>Inverted image with right position"
        />
        <p class="mb-4">
          This example demonstrates combining the invert prefix (!) with a
          position control character (&gt;). The image is both inverted and
          positioned to the right. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur
          adipiscing elit. Nullam in dui mauris. Vivamus hendrerit arcu sed erat
          molestie vehicula.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="clear-both mb-8">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">
          Combined: Invert + Full Position
        </h3>
        <Image
          src={sampleImage}
          alt="Inverted image with full position"
          title="!_Inverted image with full position"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">
          Complex Combination: Invert + Position + Style + Effect
        </h3>
        <Image
          src={sampleImage}
          alt="Complex combination example"
          title="!<Complex combination with invert, left position, glass style, and zoom effect"
          style="glass"
          effect="zoom"
        />
        <p class="mb-4">
          This example demonstrates a complex combination of features: invert,
          left position, glass style, and zoom effect. The title uses both the
          invert prefix (!) and position control character (&lt;), while the
          style and effect are set via props.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">Advanced Options</h2>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">Custom Widths</h3>
        <Image
          src={sampleImage}
          alt="Image with custom widths"
          title="Image with custom widths [300, 600, 900]"
          widths={[300, 600, 900]}
        />
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">Multiple Formats</h3>
        <Image
          src={sampleImage}
          alt="Image with multiple formats"
          title="Image with multiple formats [webp, avif]"
          formats={["webp", "avif"]}
        />
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">Custom Quality</h3>
        <Image
          src={sampleImage}
          alt="Image with custom quality"
          title="Image with custom quality (50)"
          quality={50}
        />
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">Eager Loading</h3>
        <Image
          src={sampleImage}
          alt="Image with eager loading"
          title="Image with eager loading"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">Custom Sizes Attribute</h3>
        <Image
          src={sampleImage}
          alt="Image with custom sizes attribute"
          title="Image with custom sizes attribute"
          sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 1024px) 50vw, 33vw"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium">Custom Densities</h3>
        <Image
          src={sampleImage}
          alt="Image with custom densities"
          title="Image with custom densities [1, 1.5, 2]"
          densities={[1, 1.5, 2]}
        />
      </div>
    </section>
